T1  - Continuous-Review Policies for a Multi-Echelon Inventory Problem with Stochastic Demand
AU  - De Bodt, Marc A.
AU  - Graves, Stephen C.
Y1  - 1985/10/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/10/01
